==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Europeanize
<hw>Eu`ro*pe"an*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To cause to
become like the Europeans in manners or character; to habituate or
accustom to European usages.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A state of society . . . changed and <qex>Europeanized</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Lubbock.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Europium</ent>⟦br⟧
